reviewText: I loved the series and while there are commercials on the discs, they all work and play very well. I'm mainly glad that I managed to get all the episodes! So thanks! Assuming the company decides to sell in America, I would be glad to support them but for now, I love this disc set.

I had a glowing review for this, because the show was great. But I just learned I bought a bootleg! Apparently this full collection was too good to be true, as the show was stolen, repackaged and then resold by Lambaian Filem! Do not buy like I did, support the original creators!
